OL,3,CBristol celebrates scaled-down St
OL,4,CPauls Carnival after spiralling costs
OL,6,FA series of community events have been
OL,7,Fheld in Bristol to mark a scaled-down
OL,8,Fversion St Pauls Carnival.
OL,10,FLast year more than 100,000 people
OL,11,Fattended the free event and parade,
OL,12,Fwhich celebrates African Caribbean
OL,13,Fculture, bringing an estimated nine
OL,14,Fmillion pounds into the local economy.
OL,16,FBut organisers say spiralling costs
OL,17,Fmean a parade is now only possible
OL,18,Fevery other year. It's hoped the
OL,19,Fcarnival will return in full next year.
