OL,6,FHe said: "It is a heavy load to
OL,7,Forganise but it can bring in more than
OL,8,Fnine million pounds to the city when
OL,9,Fit's on. If everyone knows what it
OL,10,Fbrings, hopefully more people can
OL,11,Fsupport it."
OL,13,FOn Saturday, a brunch was held for the
OL,14,Felders of St Pauls, some of whom
OL,15,Fhelped set up the original carnival
OL,16,Fmore than 50 years ago.
