OL,6,FBarbara Dettering, who was one of the
OL,7,Ffounders, said: "I'm very proud to see
OL,8,Fwhat we started as a little community
OL,9,Ffair has grown into this. It's getting
OL,10,Fbigger and bigger, and I was part of
OL,11,Fthat."
OL,13,FElsewhere, hundreds of people gathered
OL,14,Ffor an all day party at the Riverside
OL,15,FYouth Project, with live music and
OL,16,Ftraditional jerk chicken.
OL,18,FUnofficial celebrations were also held
OL,19,Facross St Pauls as speakers were
OL,20,Fhoisted onto scaffolding and balconies
OL,21,Fto mark carnival.
